<h2 id="create-a-github-page">Create a Github Page</h2>

<p>We will skip creating Github page tutorial and installing Jekyll theme as there are already many available contents in Google</p>

<p>I am going to use <a> https://github.com/StartBootstrap/startbootstrap-clean-blog-jekyll </a> for the tutorial.</p>

<p>Please follow the instructions on the above Github repository for installation</p>

